# Download

### Server App (C2 — old device)
Install this on the Android device you want to use as your personal cloud server.

[⬇️ Download PocketCloud Server](YOUR_LINK_HERE)

### Client App (C1 — main device)
Install this on the Android device you want to use to access your files.

[⬇️ Download PocketCloud Client](YOUR_LINK_HERE)

### Remote Access (optional)
To access your files from outside your home network, install Tailscale on both devices.

[⬇️ Download Tailscale](https://tailscale.com/download/android)
